frontMatter.title: Excelize 今天刚发布了 2.1.0 版本
frontMatter.summary: 大家好，Excelize 是 Go 语言编写的 Excel 文档基础库，今天刚发布了 2.1.0 版本，包括了很多新增功能和性能优化，希望帮助到有需要的朋友～

next.title: 图形化方式解释数学概念
next.summary: 3Blue1Brown, by Grant Sanderson, is some combination of math and entertainment, depending on your disposition. The goal is for explanations to be driven by animations and for difficult problems to be made simple with changes in perspective.
